race.description: Ladbrokes Million Dollar Chase Semi Final 6 H
race.comment: CUMBRIA JACK (2) is progressing well scoring last time out (29.04) at this track and bringing up his 15th career win. Has never missed the frame at the trip from 13 starts. Recorded the quickest time on the card last start. Will go close again if runs up to latest. WEST ROCK CASEY (8) produced an impressive win last time in quickest of the meeting when scoring by a nose (35.85) at Richmond. Should be in this for a long way. MY BOY BINGO (3) has a fair record and proved too strong last time to win by 3.5 lengths at this track in a handy 29.80 beating ICONIC JET. Sure to be thereabouts. BLACK MYTH WAVE (5) boasts a solid strike-rate over this track and distance.

Live2.SchedulerNote: Ladbrokes Million Dollar Chase Semi Final 6 H, Prize Money: $10,500
